  "title": "Quality Inspector (Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a US MNC in manufacturing industry.</strong><br /><br /><strong>Location: Tuas area</strong><br /><strong>Working Hour: Monday - Friday, 8.30am - 5.30pm</strong><br /><strong>Contract Duration: February 2026 - May 2026</strong><br /><br /><strong>Duties of Quality Inspector:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct quality inspections for incoming, in-process, and outgoing products.</li><li>Perform first-article inspections, product testing, and process/product audits.</li><li>Identify and communicate quality issues with relevant departments and follow up on corrective actions.</li><li>Maintain quality records and prepare inspection and daily reports.</li><li>Manage product release for finished goods in accordance with quality standards.</li><li>Support quality management system (QMS) initiatives and promote risk-based and process-driven practices.</li><li>Assist with other quality-related tasks as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in quality inspection.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</li></ul>",
